author: senh
title: Malheur County officials set meeting on Owyhee Canyonlands preservation plan
text: BING NEWS: Malheur County officials set meeting on Owyhee Canyonlands preservation plan Officials from Malheur County will hold a town hall meeting next week about the future of the Owhyhee Canyonlands, which make up much of the southern part of the county in southeastern Oregon. The meeting was announced in a news release from Oregon Rep.
